This folder contains the configuration files for Chombo (Make.defs.local.*)
and Hypre (doconfig.*).

Chombo:-
+ Copy the appropriate Make.defs.local.* to /path/to/Chombo/lib/mk and 
  rename it to Make.defs.local. The (*) indicates the name of the machine
  (eg: cab).

Hypre:-
+ Copy the appropriate doconfig.* to /path/to/COGENT/hypre-$VERSION/. The
  (*) indicates the machine name and the compilers to use.

